text: Rudolph V. Kuser Estate is located in Trenton, Mercer County, New Jersey, United States. The building was built in 1905 and was added to the National Register of Historic Places on August 24, 1979. ==See also== *National Register of Historic Places listings in Mercer County, New Jersey ==References== Category:Colonial Revival architecture in New Jersey Category:Houses completed in 1905 Category:Houses in Trenton, New Jersey Category:Houses on the National Register of Historic Places in New Jersey Category:National Register of Historic Places in Trenton, New Jersey Category:New Jersey Register of Historic Places Category:1905 establishments in New Jersey
